org.semanticweb.owlapi.rdf.rdfxml.parser

Class RDFParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
      • org.semanticweb.owlapi.rdf.rdfxml.parser.RDFParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IRIProvider, ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler

    public class RDFParser
extends DefaultHandler
implements IRIProvider
    This class parses the RDF according to the syntax specified in http://www.w3.org/TR/rdf- syntax-grammar/.

        object - literal object value
